nodes.text: Retep III was a planet in the Retep system.

Habassan BFF-1 bulk freighters called Starmover brought foodstuffs near the planet and the freighters Kielty were retrieving it when they were attacked by the Imperial Nebulon-B frigate Anjisan; However, Rebel Ace Keyan Farlander held off the Imperial assault until the transfer was complete.
